      <title>纳瓦尔尼盟友指责普京在立陶宛实施暴力锤击袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/navalny-ally-blames-putin-for-violent-hammer-attack-in-lithuania</link>
      <description><![CDATA[已故俄罗斯反对派领导人阿列克谢·纳瓦尔尼的一名高级助手指责总统弗拉基米尔·普京在立陶宛对他进行了锤击，并发誓要继续针对克里姆林宫进行竞选活动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/navalny-ally-blames-putin-for-violent-hammer-attack-in-lithuania</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 07:51:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国顾问指出习近平推动产业发展存在地缘政治风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/china-adviser-flags-geopolitical-risks-in-xi-s-industry-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位为政府提供咨询的著名经济学家表示，中国需要刺激内需并调整产业政策，以应对美国和欧洲对产能过剩日益增长的批评。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/china-adviser-flags-geopolitical-risks-in-xi-s-industry-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 07:17:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着军火贸易的增加，俄罗斯飞机在平壤受到制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/sanctioned-russian-plane-in-pyongyang-as-arms-trade-picks-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一家专业新闻机构报道，一架受到美国制裁的俄罗斯货机本周在平壤降落，进行一次未经宣布的旅行，引发了对非法武器转让的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/sanctioned-russian-plane-in-pyongyang-as-arms-trade-picks-up</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 07:11:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波兰图斯克将与马克龙和肖尔茨会面讨论乌克兰援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/poland-s-tusk-to-meet-macron-and-scholz-to-discuss-ukraine-aid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰总理唐纳德·图斯克表示，他将于周二在白宫与美国总统乔·拜登会谈后，于周五前往柏林，与​​法国总统马克龙和德国总理奥拉夫·肖尔茨讨论对乌克兰的援助问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/poland-s-tusk-to-meet-macron-and-scholz-to-discuss-ukraine-aid</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 06:36:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国高度评价习近平是像邓小平一样的市场改革者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/china-hails-xi-as-market-reformer-like-deng-in-sweeping-profile</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国官方媒体将习近平主席吹捧为与最高领导人邓小平齐名的市场友好型改革者，显然是为了消除对中国增长前景的怀疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/china-hails-xi-as-market-reformer-like-deng-in-sweeping-profile</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 05:04:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国在医生罢工期间提供更多医疗保健资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/south-korea-provides-more-funds-for-health-care-during-doctors-walkout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国政府筹集了更多资金来支持因数千名实习医生罢工而受到打击的医疗保健系统，随着医学生寻求缺勤以表达他们的支持，罢工范围似乎将会扩大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/south-korea-provides-more-funds-for-health-care-during-doctors-walkout</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 04:51:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>报道称，泰国总理准备辞去财务主管一职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/thai-pm-poised-to-step-aside-as-finance-minister-report-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据当地媒体报道，泰国总理斯雷塔·塔维信将辞去财政部长一职，这一变化可能会缓解与央行在货币政策方面的紧张关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/thai-pm-poised-to-step-aside-as-finance-minister-report-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 04:41:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普京称乌克兰协议需要俄罗斯做出安全承诺</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/putin-says-ukraine-deal-hinges-on-security-guarantees-for-russia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京表示，俄罗斯将要求安全保证，以考虑通过谈判结束乌克兰战争，他对一家国家通讯社表示，“实地现实”应该成为任何谈判的基础。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/putin-says-ukraine-deal-hinges-on-security-guarantees-for-russia</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 03:15:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>紧张局势一触即发，拜登着眼于中国造船补贴</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/biden-says-us-to-review-union-petition-on-china-shipbuilding</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统乔·拜登承诺调查一组工会的请愿书，要求他的政府审查中国对造船厂的补贴，因为在关键的美国大选年，世界最大的两个经济体之间在贸易和关键供应链上的紧张局势不断加剧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/biden-says-us-to-review-union-petition-on-china-shipbuilding</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 01:44:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚称中国提议终止惩罚性葡萄酒关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/china-issues-draft-to-end-australia-wine-tariffs-winemaker-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚葡萄酒商和立法者表示，中国提议取消对该国葡萄酒的惩罚性关税，这表明随着两国寻求加强关系，为期三年的贸易争端即将结束。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/china-issues-draft-to-end-australia-wine-tariffs-winemaker-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 09:39:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
